-> install screenshot software
sudo pacman -S spectacle --needed

-> install dolphin and ffmpegthumbs
sudo pacman -S dolphin ffmpegthumbs --needed

-> disable compositor vsync
/home/user/.config/plasma-workspace/env/kwin.sh
KWIN_X11_NO_SYNC_TO_VBLANK=1
KWIN_X11_REFRESH_RATE=144000
KWIN_X11_FORCE_SOFTWARE_VSYNC=1

-> use picom compositor
https://wiki.archlinux.org/title/Picom
sudo pacman -S picom
configure picom, then autostart

-> to disable and enable kwin compositor need qdbus
sudo pacman -S qt5-tools --needed

-> disable kwallet
~/.config/kwalletrc
[Wallet]
Enabled=false

-> unbind meta key from application launcher
~/.config/kwinrc
[ModifierOnlyShortcuts]
Meta=

-> bind meta key to krunner
https://wiki.archlinux.org/title/KRunner

-> arc theme
yay -S arc-kde --needed

-> remove discover from system tray
/etc/pacman.conf
NoExtract = etc/xdg/autostart/org.kde.discover.notifier.desktop
then remove /etc/xdg/autostart/org.kde.discover.notifier.desktop

-> tiling windows with gaps
https://github.com/gikari/bismuth/blob/master/TWEAKS.md
sudo pacman -S kwin-bismuth --needed
